&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.amazon.com/Tango-Our-Dance-Estela-Arcos/dp/B000EMGIQE/ref=sr_1_4?ie=UTF8&amp;amp;s=dvd&amp;amp;qid=1240151465&amp;amp;sr=8-4&#34;&gt;Tango: bayle nuestro&lt;/a&gt; (Great milongueros dancing footage)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.amazon.com/Tango-Obsession-Documentary-Carlos-Copes/dp/B000W6D1AS/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;amp;s=dvd&amp;amp;qid=1240151848&amp;amp;sr=8-1&#34;&gt;Tango the obsession&lt;/a&gt; (Milongueros dancing footage)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://cgi.ebay.com/TANGO-UN-GIRO-EXTRANO-MERCEDES-GARCIA-GUEVARA-NEW_W0QQitemZ180323902894QQcmdZViewItemQQptZUS_DVD_HD_DVD_Blu_ray?hash=item180323902894&amp;amp;_trksid=p4634.c0.m14.l1262&#34;&gt;Un giro extraño&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;El confitería Ideal (BBC documentary, not available commercially, see &lt;a href=&#34;http://simbatango.com/2008/09/23/confiteria-la-ideal-en-bbc/&#34;&gt;earlier post&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

