&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.amazon.com/Tango-Lesson-Region-2/dp/B00005KIVN/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;amp;s=dvd&amp;amp;qid=1240151425&amp;amp;sr=8-1&#34;&gt;Tango lesson&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

